  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>原创 <span>每日发现最新LLM</span> <span>2025-10-24 18:04</span> <span style=\"display: inline-block;\">中国香港</span></p>\n  <p>3D生成项目OmniPart，代码生成模型GLM-4.6-REAP，人工智能推动系统研究的项目ADRS，模型压缩工具包AngelSlim，框架AceSearcher，Agent框架AgentFlow</p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cf3a8a97&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzvLOZiaOfsa0nDTeKdcQGUtqV6iacyMwlBdtyLJN1iccSxFFcIic7ibXvIJAwVlpibWJKaXp4xW408ichWg%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"text-align: center;line-height: normal;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: normal;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100010333\" data-ratio=\"0.0859375\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;width: 389px;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=17b00053&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwuWicsSRFbFewfePZ1EiaVdtFvrJflfNa3P11kpGn8dhrOaAmmKQ3INqCXFZr2IrrUmmtkia9otecsw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif\"></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆基座模型</span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：OmniPart</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"482\" data-imgfileid=\"100016330\" data-type=\"png\" data-width=\"1166\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-w=\"1080\" data-ratio=\"0.412962962962963\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6b6939fa&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzvLOZiaOfsa0nDTeKdcQGUtCEyApibkdYRocbVjibxv2Eeck9u20D5iaHfoU7T2V7qC2xyRLjG0h0kibw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★OmniPart是一个面向3D生成的项目，旨在通过语义解耦和结构凝聚实现部件感知的3D生成。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目提供了预训练模型、交互式演示、训练代码和数据处理工具，支持用户在3D生成任务中实现更高效的部件级别控制和生成。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/omnipart\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/omnipart</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：GLM-4.6-REAP</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"512\" data-imgfileid=\"100016332\" data-type=\"png\" data-width=\"1170\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-w=\"1080\" data-ratio=\"0.43796296296296294\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f0bac769&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzvLOZiaOfsa0nDTeKdcQGUtHORSdVLyQ240zSSt5ibO9d2eheGCHn4bFpm0kotLzf4MnAtjLYxbCuw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★GLM-4.6-REAP</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">适用于代码生成、代理编码和函数调用等任务，特别适合资源受限的环境和本地部署。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该模型</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">是GLM-4.6-FP8的压缩版本，采用了REAP（Router-weighted Expert Activation Pruning）方法进行专家剪枝，减少了40%的参数量，同时保持了几乎相同的性能。该模型适用于代码生成、代理编码和函数调用等任务，特别适合资源受限的环境和本地部署。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/glm-4-6-reap\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/glm-4-6-reap</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🛠️框架平台、必备工具</span></strong></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：ADRS</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"640\" data-imgfileid=\"100016331\" data-type=\"png\" data-width=\"1170\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-w=\"1080\" data-ratio=\"0.5472222222222223\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a509b5c1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzvLOZiaOfsa0nDTeKdcQGUtmWI4ZliaumfHJ97IGicLmwTvfgX8CicpqapUq1ZlcSubpDlXuRwtWiaA1A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★AI-Driven Research For Systems (ADRS) 是一个专注于通过人工智能推动系统研究的项目。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目展示了在多个框架和领域中应用AI进行系统任务的研究示例，包括专家放置、全局模型调度、事务调度、遥测修复、LLM-SQL优化、单区域和多区域的现货实例调度、多区域数据传输、稀疏注意力设计以及多代理系统设计等。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/adrs\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/adrs</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：AngelSlim</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"390\" data-imgfileid=\"100016329\" data-type=\"png\" data-width=\"1168\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-w=\"1080\" data-ratio=\"0.33425925925925926\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=908bed1a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzvLOZiaOfsa0nDTeKdcQGUtjULvCt9uuzg2H8BUXGFUSF9EDweZMgMHgrZGLKNZDFKAjaIZbx8qibA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★AngelSlim是一个专为提高可用性、全面性和效率而设计的模型压缩工具包。它集成了主流的压缩算法，支持一键式调用，具有良好的易用性</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">。该工具包不仅集成了广泛使用的工业算法，还持续自研更优的压缩算法，并逐步开源。AngelSlim在模型压缩流程和算法部署方面进行了端到端优化，支持多种量化方法和模型。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/angelslim3\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/angelslim3</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">③项目：AceSearcher</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"880\" data-imgfileid=\"100016333\" data-type=\"png\" data-width=\"1058\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-w=\"1058\" data-ratio=\"0.831758034026465\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1f1a68f7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzvLOZiaOfsa0nDTeKdcQGUtMPYpKblf8GHwq6aw2lluLmCLKWfYsKp2uXL2aYzJgINh5aiccvYlWoQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★AceSearcher是一个框架，通过增强自我对弈统一大语言模型（LLMs）的推理和搜索能力。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该方法通过联合训练分解器和求解器模块，利用监督微调和增强学习阶段，提升LLMs解决多跳推理任务的能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/acesearcher\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/acesearcher</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🤖 Agent开发</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：AgentFlow</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"596\" data-imgfileid=\"100016334\" data-type=\"png\" data-width=\"1168\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-w=\"1080\" data-ratio=\"0.5101851851851852\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4f56c31e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzvLOZiaOfsa0nDTeKdcQGUtzEujZia0L26YzYMUMKWI2Ph9H8L6sFJg6hPrgmDKMvFW2oLVFZP0nMA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★AgentFlow是一个可训练的、工具集成的Agent框架，旨在克服当前工具增强推理方法的可扩展性和泛化性限制。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">与传统方法不同，AgentFlow引入了一个模块化Agent系统，包含四个专门模块：规划器、执行器、验证器和生成器。该框架通过在线方式直接优化系统内的规划Agent，使用基于流的群体优化策略（Flow-GRPO），在多领域中实现了卓越的性能，提升了工具调用的可靠性和长期推理能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/agentflow3\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/agentflow3</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: center;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span style=\"padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"908\" data-imgfileid=\"100012181\" data-ratio=\"1.5712962962962962\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" da